1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Shadow Verify — fully local, no network, no upload.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Valid bundle: record integrity, signature, hash chain, profile all VERIFIED.

3
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Analytical correctness is NOT judged — a signature proves integrity, not correctness.

4
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Limitations: what verification does and does not prove.

5
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Tampered bundle FAILS at the exact sequence; downstream flagged; no false green.

6
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:23,000
Verify the verifier: FIXTURE-signed manifest — assets match, but INDEPENDENT COMPARISON NOT PERFORMED.

7
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:37,000
Tampered manifest: ASSET MISMATCH with expected/actual hashes — no generic trusted badge.

8
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:53,000
Simplified Chinese: same evidence values, localized UI only.
